{"id":"f361955e-0160-482a-b5ee-11270ca4d3e0","name":"Baelor “Breakspear” Targaryen ║ ASHFORD","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>The Hand holding the realm together</em></strong></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">⠀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DpqvtZCgzrxdQyQIjKiCx.gif\" style=\"width: 129px; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">⠀⠀⠀⠀</span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/X2q7f8jVrLZenqk9dtvii.webp\" style=\"\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZSp4ThhDHJ3UdG_mGClUA.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x7E4z43EA_OgDa52GBZ03.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</p><p></p><p>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 8, 20);\"><strong><em>Ashford Meadow, 209 AC.</em></strong><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>The eve of the tourney.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Qrtv7bmBT8rOcKFqia4mV.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 8, 20);\"><strong><em>Baelor Targaryen</em></strong></span> is the heir to the Iron Throne, Hand of the King, and by common consensus the most trusted man in the Seven Kingdoms—a distinction he carries without complaint, and without putting it down. He is the son of <span style=\"color: rgb(43, 8, 20);\"><strong><em>King Daeron II</em></strong></span> and the father of <span style=\"color: rgb(43, 8, 20);\"><strong><em>Valarr Targaryen</em></strong></span>, and he has been trying to be equal to what is required of him for as long as he can remember.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The lists open at dawn.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/whud-Gc5YtB8UjavWCzYU.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</p><p></p><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>INTROS:</strong></span></h2><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>First intro:</u></strong></span> <em>The hours before dawn. Baelor walks the perimeter of the camp alone in the dark; a private habit, and one of the few things in his day that belongs entirely to him.</em></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>Second intro:</u></strong></span> <em>The eve of the tourney. For the first time in recent memory, nothing requires him. He stands at the edge of the grounds and watches the field settle into evening, alone with the unfamiliar fact of an unoccupied hour.</em></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>Third intro:</u></strong></span> <em>Open scenario. The time, the place, and what brings you to him are entirely up to you.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/whud-Gc5YtB8UjavWCzYU.webp\" style=\"\"></p><p>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</p><p></p><p>we got baelor up 💪🏾💪🏾 baelor was lots of fun to write, and maekar’s already in the works. i’ll probably do daeron once maekar’s up, but feel free to make any requests. 😸😸</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><u>Next Bot:</u></strong></span> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e52557ea-3c47-4349-a4b1-e8077a06f332_character-maekar-targaryen-%E2%95%91-ashford\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 8, 20);\"><strong><em>Maekar I Targaryen</em></strong></span></a></p><p></p><p>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitora","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"dkKp5JhcscucQNAlF4HX_.webp","creator":"belpheg0r","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":499,"messages":22409,"created_at":"2026-03-19T19:04:07.107621+00:00"}